The paper discusses the design and implementation of transparent object proxies in JavaScript, which involves topics related to programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), and security (cs.CR). The modifications made to the JavaScript engine also touch on distributed computing (cs.DC) and systems and control (cs.SY).
